page.title: 20Compilation Group.
page.content: Data for this block was compiled by the children in the upper junior class of Bickleigh C of E School:_ Mark Scantlebury, Alan Hunkin, Simon Hatherley, Heath Cook, Andrew Edwards, Andrew Ball, Neil Sarjantson, B.J. Purdy, Tamsin Gaudie, Sarah Barber, Lisa Thomas, Adele Hannaford, Kerri Campbell, Sophie Brain, Kim Walker, Elizabeth Herd, Claire Britchfield,Anne Pedrick, and Timothy Ritson. The children vary in age between eight and eleven years. The data was edited and presented by Bridget Macdonald and Barrie Hyne, staff at the school.
